s, I probably didn't want that kind of guy.  And still they pestered me.<br>
<br>
Okay... I know that was long.  This topic really does bother me, though, because I see girls selling themsleves short for just a little bit of unneeded attention.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :intel --><img src=http://heartjoys.fcpages.com/Sparrow'sHearth/znaika.gif ALT=":intel"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I see it in church every week, and I just want to cry.  I would love to tell them what that guy is really thinking, and that 9 times out of 10 it has nothing to do with the Bible.  I see it at school, and I see it when I go to the mall.  My heart breaks for these girls.  They need to know they are valued without having to wear the sexually explicit clothes they wear.  This doesn't value them at all, in fact, it devalues them... and that's when bad things happen to girls. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :intel --><img src=http://heartjoys.fcpages.com/Sparrow'sHearth/znaika.gif ALT=":intel"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Okay.. off my soapbox, for now, anyway. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bsparrowshearth.showUserPublicProfile?gid=heartjoys>heartjoys</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=purple><b>Velvet-Steel Wannabe</b></font></span><br>  Posts: 2097<br> <font color=#B87333>(12/31/03 2:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fsparrowshearthfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=29.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://heartjoys.fcpages.com/Sparrow'sHearth/celticcross.jpeg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What Women Wear</span><hr size=1> I appreciate you sharing of your experiences <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Mallaidh08</strong><!--EZCODE BOL